   ->  Index Scan using ck_p1_pkey on ck_p1 (actual rows=1 loops=1)
         Index Cond: (k = 1)
         Storage Table Read Requests: 1
         Storage Table Read Ops: 1
         Storage Table Rows Scanned: 1
         Storage Table Write Requests: 2
 Storage Read Requests: 1
